    %% Bindings
    SA_Controller -->|bound via| CRB_Manager
    SA_Controller -->|bound via| CRB_MetricsAuth
    SA_Controller -->|bound via| RB_Leader
    SA_Prometheus -->|bound via| CRB_MetricsReader
    SA_EPP -->|bound via| CRB_EPP

    CRB_Manager -->|grants| CR_Manager
    CRB_MetricsAuth -->|grants| CR_MetricsAuth
    CRB_MetricsReader -->|grants| CR_MetricsReader
    RB_Leader -->|grants| R_Leader

    %% manager-role permissions
    CR_Manager -->|access| ConfigMaps
    CR_Manager -->|access| ConfigMapsStatus
    CR_Manager -->|access| Events
    CR_Manager -->|access| NSPodsSvcSecrets
    CR_Manager -->|access| Nodes
    CR_Manager -->|access| Deployments
