    CR_Manager -->|access| LWSScale
    CR_Manager -->|access| VA
    CR_Manager -->|access| VAFinalizers
    CR_Manager -->|access| VAStatus
    CR_Manager -->|access| ServiceMonitors

    %% metrics-auth-role permissions
    CR_MetricsAuth -->|access| TokenReviews
    CR_MetricsAuth -->|access| SAR

    %% metrics-reader-role permissions
    CR_MetricsReader -->|access| MetricsURL

    %% leader-election-role permissions
    R_Leader -->|access| LE_ConfigMaps
    R_Leader -->|access| LE_Leases
    R_Leader -->|access| LE_Events

